09 July 2007

Version 0.0.11.  Bug fixes and support for FLAC 1.1.4.
Tested on Mac OS 10.4.9 (Macports 1.442), FreeBSD 6.2, Ubuntu 7.0.4

08 May 2005

Version 0.0.9.  SIGINT (control-C) plays next song; two in succession exits.
improved --help message.

18 Feb 2005

Version 0.0.8.  fixed 8 bit support.  tested with FLAC 1.1.2 on 
Mac OS 10.3.8 (Fink 0.23.3), FreeBSD 5.3, Redhat 9.0, Fedora Core 3

04 Mar 2004

Version 0.0.7.  opportunistic ao_close to reduce inter-track gap.

29 Feb 2004

Version 0.0.6.  compiles on Yellowdog Linux 3.0.1 and Mac OS 10.3.2 with Fink.

18 Jan 2004

Version 0.0.5 available.  compiles on FreeBSD.

01 Jan 2004

Version 0.0.4 available.  now supports wav file output.

23 Nov 2003

Version 0.0.3 available.  works with irmp3!

16 Nov 2003

Version 0.0.2 available.  alpha version of remote mode complete.

26 Oct 2003

flac123 is back from the dead!  Version 0.0.1 available.  Compiles on
Redhat 9.0 against libao-0.8.3 and FLAC 1.1.0.
